{"tid":306512,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（yoyo)林伯豪宅淪變態樂園　37歲中女陪客吸毒玩SM","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T09:22:47.000Z","uid":3806,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f62d198fa92b20cf7e1e22d0b8d82dfa22f37a26","tid":306512,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"租霸每個地方都有，不過租樓畀人搞到自己間屋淪為變態淫竇，就真係陰公喇！英國《太陽報》大爆，林柏特位於倫敦嘅價值200萬鎊(約2,034萬港元)豪宅，以月租3,400鎊租咗畀一個叫達雲娜(Davina Ward)嘅37歲中女健身教練。<br />\n<br />\n由於對方自稱係健身教練，所以林柏特冇咩介心，點知達雲娜原來喺單位內提供另類服務，喺網上用Diverse Stacey呢個名開檔。佢嘅服務包括同人客玩SM，綁起同鞭打人哋，每小時盛惠400鎊，而且有優惠套餐，加多100鎊就可以拍埋片。《太陽報》記者放蛇扮成顧客，入咗呢間200萬淫宅，達雲娜不知有詐，帶記者行咗幾間有晒「主題」嘅房，仲向記者提供毒品：「如果我賣畀你，我就犯咗法，所以你陣間畀番多少貼士我啦！」事後化驗證實，「林伯豪宅SM女王」提供嘅係可卡因。 <br />\n<br />\n林伯一家住所離「變態豪宅」只係2英里，但係完全唔知自己間屋畀人咁樣反轉法，所以呢位英格蘭名將身邊嘅朋友話，林伯知道真相後，已經講明會立即處理，以免有麻煩上身喇！ <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170702/photo/bkn-20170702130547861-0702_00882_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20170702%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170702130547861-0702_00882_001_01p.jpg&h=8dcdcae2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8192d2cb318b79fe7cfc2d4ba48c23690d9ae01e","tid":306512,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"@蓋清"},{"pid":"19ca1ecaec33d221c2972d51f29cec0d0ba1419c","tid":306512,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"個記者係咪試晒啲服務"},{"pid":"6755d8b5cbf78c1f4ac17e286c7c8d1385bcc8cc","tid":306512,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:08:17.000Z","msg":"有冇ching組團"},{"pid":"8b35ec18aa2a4b8a93f1cd03658b82ad5a5f6862","tid":306512,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"林伯自己都玩過啦 點會唔知"},{"pid":"df7b0f059d03962ac8333ac266d7aa64ecd88f03","tid":306512,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:15:23.000Z","msg":"每個月玩一次當交下租"},{"pid":"3b5504515039d8d2c7e2b0f63e11514570369ac2","tid":306512,"uid":37811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"蓋清帶團去試玩?"},{"pid":"ec88c35b8c2bdc09fbc1068284073ce842e1fb21","tid":306512,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"麻友竇"},{"pid":"f9f470419917305190d346b983919b1d4d155d98","tid":306512,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"瀨屎狗!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"59df8af66dbb35952795415d4589f13f30e74c4b","tid":306512,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蓋清帶團去試玩?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8afc0b88bca2f228caa9ee1ff04cd2d5f5a2bcf","tid":306512,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"1負皮"},{"pid":"068f0cf6a7b309dbd50e2d2ec71c1779af4e2ad0","tid":306512,"uid":101804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:07:19.000Z","msg":"條女好似幾正"},{"pid":"6948640539b4dbbe153b8f2435470d6ff93790dd","tid":306512,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f250d53d3b7887e3321235b71080566cc1d5df4b","tid":306512,"uid":31173,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"屌以為邊個林伯豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a567c883347fe01b33c9d6a9531931d205c84e0","tid":306512,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"女租客無錢交租，我叫她。。。"},{"pid":"e28543ec88e0ca075358cce5d0feed6d094fa269","tid":306512,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif